Compatibility-surface module notice

`src/ait_native/**` is a compatibility package and does not have one uniform
license posture across every shim.

Use `docs/legal/module_license_map.md` as the source of truth for the current
submodule-by-submodule mapping:
- local/trust-layer compatibility shims follow Apache-2.0
- server/worker compatibility shims follow AGPL-3.0-only OR LicenseRef-AIT-Commercial
- web compatibility shims follow LicenseRef-AIT-Commercial by default
